CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 27, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "The Glamorous Cotillion - Scenes from the third annual debutante Cotillion given by Pittsburgh AKAs...center, the glamorous debutantes of 1954 pose for the photographer..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young woman wearing light colored strapless gown with lace overlay and ruching on bodice with sweetheart neckline and light colored gloves, and young man wearing tuxedo with tails, gloves, and pocket scarf, standing in Syria Mosque of Alpha Kappa Alpha's 1954 Cotillion
